        <ul>
          <li>üîç In-depth AI girlfriend app comparisons</li>
          <li>üìñ Guides on getting the most from your AI companion</li>
          <li>üÜï Latest app updates and new releases</li>
          <li>üí° Tips for building meaningful AI relationships</li>
          <li>üîí Privacy and safety advice</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="subscribe-cta">Subscribe to our newsletter to be notified when we publish new content!</p>
        <form class="newsletter-subscribe">
          <input type="email" placeholder="Enter your email" required />
          <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Notify Me</button>
        </form>
      </div>

      <div class="featured-apps">
        <h2>While You Wait, Explore Our Top Picks</h2>
        <div class="quick-links">
          <a href="/#reviews" class="quick-link-card glass-card">
            <span class="link-icon">‚≠ê</span>
